          "value": "11h drive / 14h window"
        },
        {
          "fact_id": "GT275-US-HOU-002",
          "text": "Property-carrying drivers may not drive after 60/70 hours on duty in 7/8 consecutive days; a 34-hour restart may reset the weekly limit when used per Part 395.",
